      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "There are some checks for Unicode before in the file here. So, if this is being enforced we should cleanup that code here to be consistent. \r\nhttps://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/2d4749b366c4cae3da19017d6658f11349634303/test/functional/test_runner.py#L33. \r\nAt the very least, we can change the dirname.  We are introducing this dependency just for a directory name whereas at other places we checks for it . If the project ends up really using UTF-8 command line arguments, maybe it can be enforced at that time. ",
